GDB
===

https://www.gnu.org/software/gdb/

## Intro 

$ gcc -g segfault.c -o segfault
$ gdb segfault

run program
(gdb) r

list sources of a function
(gdb) list main

set breakpoint to a function
(gdb) b main

set breakpoint to a line in a file
(gdb) b segfault.c:87

continue
(gdb) c

next statement
(gdb) n

print
(gdb) p i

display (print in each next)
(gdb) disp i

quit
(gdb) q

